============== Passives ===========
Magic Resistance: The pixie has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects
Innate Spellcasting: The pixie's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 12). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring only its pixie dust as a component: At will: druidcraft 1/day each: confusion, dancing lights, detect evil and good, detect thoughts, dispel magic, entangle, fly, phantasmal force, polymorph, sleep
Superior Invisibility: As an action, the pixie magically turns invisible until its concentration ends (as if concentrating on a spell). Any equipment the pixie wears or carries is invisible with it
========== Attacks null ========
